              <h5 class="card-title">St Tropez / Vienna</h5>
              <p class="card-text">My name is Philippe Beaulieu I have grown up in the south of France. I have always loved music since I was born, I play the guitar,
                the piano, I sing. I used to play and sing in a rock band and was making music on every possible occasion.
                When I was 15 I discovered the art of DJing, back then I was working on a private beach in St Tropez and I was playing ambient music on vinyl
                during the sunset, I alway loved to take people on a journey with my music. My job life took me furthermore to New York, Paris and Vienna
                where I was playing on a regular basis at private parties but also at nightclub venues, playing for friends and for promoters, that appreciate
                my quite unusual music selection.What I like is to take people on a journey in a beautiful location and enhance strong emotions and positive
                vibes with my DJ sets.</p>
            </div>
